Printable View in Case Feed

Use the printable view option to view and print a comprehensive list of the information related to a case.

Available in: Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs)
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Printable view displays:

Case details
Contents of related lists that are included on the Case Detail page
Internal notes
Notes and Tips

Customize your Case Detail page layouts to add Activity History related list for emails and call logs. 
Include public portal posts by adding Case Comments related list.

Internal notes are listed under Chatter.
Related lists without data aren’t displayed.
Custom links and buttons appear in case details section.
Printable view shows 500 each of recent internal note posts, links, and documents, and 100 comments on these posts.
